odreporter.com/lists/2017-tca-award-nominations-1014665|accessdate=25 June 2017|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=19 June 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180219090235/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/2017-tca-award-nominations-1014665|archive-date=19 February 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Variety Talk Series]]\n| {{won}}\n| rowspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=\"Emmys\" />\n|-\n| [[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Writing for a Variety Series]]\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Interactive Program]]\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"10\"|2018\n| [[Dorian Awards|Dorian Award for TV Current Affairs Show of the Year]]\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite news|last1=Kilday|first1=Gregg|title='Call Me by Your Name' Leads Dorian Award Nominations|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/call-me-by-your-name-leads-dorian-award-nominations-1073577|accessdate=19 January 2018|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=10 January 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180110234338/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/call-me-by-your-name-leads-dorian-award-nominations-1073577|archive-date=10 January 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n|colspan=2|[[Dorian Awards|Dorian Award for Wilde Wit of the Year]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Producers Guild of America Awards 2017|Producers Guild of America Award for Outstanding Producer of Live Entertainment & Talk Television]]\n| rowspan=\"9\"|''Last Week Tonight with John Oliver''\n| {{won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|last1=Swertlow|first1=Meg|title=Producers Guild Awards 2018 Winners: The Complete List|url=https://www.eonline.com/news/907738/producers-guild-awards-2018-winners-the-complete-list|website=E! News|accessdate=21 January 2018|date=20 January 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180121092930/http://www.eonline.com/news/907738/producers-guild-awards-2018-winners-the-comple